{"tid":195629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登上報] 名媛自資出版童書影射日人為「東洋妖怪」","createTime":"2017-04-10T17:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T14:21:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b90997f6c0b4453eecb67ca776b10b94d4ee79a","tid":195629,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:44:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/名媛自資出版童書宣傳反日-影射日人為-東洋妖怪-蘿蔔洋鬼子-主角率眾踢爛-胖國神社/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%90%8D%E5%AA%9B%E8%87%AA%E8%B3%87%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E7%AB%A5%E6%9B%B8%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E5%8F%8D%E6%97%A5-%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%84%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%BA-%E6%9D%B1%E6%B4%8B%E5%A6%96%E6%80%AA-%E8%98%BF%E8%94%94%E6%B4%8B%E9%AC%BC%E5%AD%90-%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%92%E7%8E%87%E7%9C%BE%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%9B-%E8%83%96%E5%9C%8B%E7%A5%9E%E7%A4%BE%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=7cab7090\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%90%8D%E5%AA%9B%E8%87%AA%E8%B3%87%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E7%AB%A5%E6%9B%B8%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E5%8F%8D%E6%97%A5-%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%84%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%BA%E7%82%BA-%E6%9D%B1%E6%B4%8B%E5%A6%96%E6%80%AA-%E8%98%BF%E8%94%94%E6%B4%8B%E9%AC%BC%E5%AD%90-%E4%B8%BB%E8%A7%92%E7%8E%87%E7%9C%BE%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%9B-%E8%83%96%E5%9C%8B%E7%A5%9E%E7%A4%BE%2F&h=8aec06e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/名媛自資出版童書宣傳反日-影射日人為-東洋妖怪-蘿蔔洋鬼子-主角率眾踢爛-胖國神社/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/red-17_ck6zq_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fred-17_ck6zq_1200x0.png&h=c2029872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有網民在「連登討論區」貼出一套名為《南山七小福》的童書，內容充斥影射日本的內容，當中主角打敗「東洋妖怪」、「東洋鬼子」，並出現「日之國邪惡首相」等奸角，質疑該系列童書有煽動種族仇恨、向學童灌輸仇恨教育之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n《南》系列作者朱穎詩為王氏國際集團第三代後人、仁濟醫院副主席王賢訊（Vincent）妻子，向兒童讀者自稱「Vincci 姐姐」。書中故事則由王賢訊負責構思。朱又曾與其夫在社交網站上，上載與中聯辦副主任譚鐵牛，以及候任特首林鄭月娥的合照，唯有關照片目前已設為非公開。<br />\n<br />\n《南山七小福》至今已出版至第 21 集，其中多集均有影射日本的內容。在第 6-7 集「七小福大戰東洋妖怪」中，出現主角群怒斥「東洋鬼子太無恥，憎透他們！」，自稱「不畏東洋鬼子」，到「釣龜島」宣示主權，「打敗鬼子妖怪為我國人民出一口氣」、「收拾東洋妖怪」奪回「釣龜島」等情節。<br />\n<br />\n而在第 15-16 集「七小福反轉胖國神社」，則大篇幅影射靖國神社及日本修憲兩項議題，出現「日之國邪惡首相加倍晉餐」、副首相「麻疹太郎」等奸角，書中出現主角群將「胖國神社」內所有神主牌破壞得「片甲不留」的情境。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">作者為仁濟副主席妻　自資出版「讓孩子吸收中國傳統文化意識」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n《南山七小福》系列書籍自「南山文化」出版，該出版社為王氏夫婦自資成立。朱㯋詩在接受訪問時曾稱，目前香港童書市場上大多是外國作品，在丈夫支持下，決定出版「富有中國傳統文化特色」的故事書，將中國不同神祇卡通化。訪問中朱又透露，在《南》系列出版後，她曾主動聯絡港九新界百多間小學進行講座，以吸引更多讀者，「使孩子們吸收中國傳統文化意識，教育從幼苗開始」。"},{"pid":"fdb09f09ff6ced0d5b06fd508eecac0b94f823ef","tid":195629,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/17857698_10154223544082827_1677619219_n_Z3tqE_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F17857698_10154223544082827_1677619219_n_Z3tqE_1200x0.jpg&h=89f84228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王賢訊與朱穎詩夫婦與林鄭月娥合照　（王賢訊IG專頁）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/IMG_20170410_185517_j3ia2_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FIMG_20170410_185517_j3ia2_1200x0.jpg&h=b839a92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/jaklsdjklasjdkla_lqjDR_1200x0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjaklsdjklasjdkla_lqjDR_1200x0.JPG&h=2873d50f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/ajksldjaklsjdklasjdklas_GTWMx_1200x0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fajksldjaklsjdklasjdklas_GTWMx_1200x0.JPG&h=60b3d5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestand